          "source_html": "<div class=\"group\">\n            <h4>Questions 1–7</h4>\n            <p>Do the following statements agree with the information given in Reading Passage 1? In boxes 1–7 write <strong>TRUE, FALSE or NOT GIVEN</strong>.</p>\n\n            <div id=\"q1-anchor\" class=\"question-block\">\n                <p class=\"question-text\">1. According to Gregory of Tours, the landslide which caused the flood happened near Tauredunum.</p>\n                <div class=\"yesno-group\">\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"TRUE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(1)\"> TRUE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"FALSE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(1)\"> FALSE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"NOT GIVEN\" onchange=\"markAnswered(1)\"> NOT GIVEN</label>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"q2-anchor\" class=\"question-block\">\n                <p class=\"question-text\">2. The city of Geneva was undamaged by the tsunami that Gregory described.</p>\n                <div class=\"yesno-group\">\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"TRUE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(2)\"> TRUE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"FALSE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(2)\"> FALSE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"NOT GIVEN\" onchange=\"markAnswered(2)\"> NOT GIVEN</label>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"q3-anchor\" class=\"question-block\">\n                <p class=\"question-text\">3. The work of Marius of Avenches supported the idea that there was a tsunami.</p>\n                <div class=\"yesno-group\">\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"TRUE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(3)\"> TRUE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"FALSE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(3)\"> FALSE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"NOT GIVEN\" onchange=\"markAnswered(3)\"> NOT GIVEN</label>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"q4-anchor\" class=\"question-block\">\n                <p class=\"question-text\">4. The rocks which fell into the delta were very hard and dense.</p>\n                <div class=\"yesno-group\">\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"TRUE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(4)\"> TRUE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"FALSE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(4)\"> FALSE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"NOT GIVEN\" onchange=\"markAnswered(4)\"> NOT GIVEN</label>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"q5-anchor\" class=\"question-block\">\n                <p class=\"question-text\">5. Richard Schweickert has published studies on lake tsunamis that have occurred in several countries.</p>\n                <div class=\"yesno-group\">\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"TRUE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(5)\"> TRUE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"FALSE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(5)\"> FALSE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"NOT GIVEN\" onchange=\"markAnswered(5)\"> NOT GIVEN</label>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"q6-anchor\" class=\"question-block\">\n                <p class=\"question-text\">6. The shoreline of Lake Tahoe has remained unchanged for 20,000 years.</p>\n                <div class=\"yesno-group\">\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"TRUE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(6)\"> TRUE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"FALSE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(6)\"> FALSE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"NOT GIVEN\" onchange=\"markAnswered(6)\"> NOT GIVEN</label>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"q7-anchor\" class=\"question-block\">\n                <p class=\"question-text\">7. Parts of the population of Geneva now live closer to the lake than was the case in the sixth century.</p>\n                <div class=\"yesno-group\">\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"TRUE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(7)\"> TRUE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"FALSE\" onchange=\"markAnswered(7)\"> FALSE</label>\n                    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"NOT GIVEN\" onchange=\"markAnswered(7)\"> NOT GIVEN</label>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
