          "source_html": "<div class=\"group\">\n            <h4>Questions 8–13</h4>\n            <p>Complete the flow-chart below. Choose <strong>ONE WORD AND/OR A NUMBER</strong> from the passage for each answer.</p>\n            <p><strong>The evidence for a tsunami in Lake Geneva</strong></p>\n\n            <div id=\"q8-anchor\" class=\"flowchart-item\">\n                <span class=\"flowchart-text\">Katrina Kremer was looking for indications of prehistoric</span>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"q8\" placeholder=\"(one word)\" oninput=\"markAnswered(8)\" name=\"q8\">\n                <span>that had occurred before the sixth-century event.</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flowchart-item\">\n                <span class=\"flowchart-text\">Instead her research team found a large lens-shaped deposit.</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flowchart-item\">\n                <span class=\"flowchart-text\">Researchers extracted samples from the deposit and dated organic material such as</span>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"q9\" placeholder=\"(one word)\" oninput=\"markAnswered(9)\" name=\"q9\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flowchart-item\">\n                <span class=\"flowchart-text\">Carbon-dating confirmed that the deposit was present in the lake by the beginning of the</span>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"q10\" placeholder=\"(e.g. fifth)\" oninput=\"markAnswered(10)\" name=\"q10\">\n                <span>century.</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flowchart-item\">\n                <span class=\"flowchart-text\">The volume of the deposit was then</span>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"q11\" placeholder=\"(one word)\" oninput=\"markAnswered(11)\" name=\"q11\">\n                <span>by the scientists.</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flowchart-item\">\n                <span class=\"flowchart-text\">The researchers established the approximate</span>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"q12\" placeholder=\"(one word)\" oninput=\"markAnswered(12)\" name=\"q12\">\n                <span>and speed of the tsunami through extensive computer modelling.</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flowchart-item\">\n                <span class=\"flowchart-text\">A likely cause of the rockfall was a significant</span>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"q13\" placeholder=\"(one word)\" oninput=\"markAnswered(13)\" name=\"q13\">\n            </div>\n        </div>",
